          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-b4fb48cc26c4274f",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "CDIC deposit insurance.\nLaurentian Bank of Canada is a member of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation (CDIC). Our subsidiaries, LBC Trust and Laurentian Trust of Canada Inc., are also CDIC members in their own right.\nThe CDIC is a federal Crown corporation that protects eligible deposits payable in Canada at each CDIC member institution up to a maximum of $100,000 (principal and interest combined, calculated in Canadian dollars) per insured category.\nFor more information about how your deposits are protected, contact the CDIC at 1-800-461-2342 or visit cdic.ca . For details, read the CDIC abbreviated brochure (PDF, 67 KB) .\ncdic.ca\nCDIC abbreviated brochure (PDF, 67 KB)\nCDIC member information",
