          "evidence_text_excerpt": "3. Calculate cash in and cash out.\nBudgeting is about knowing what kind of flexibility you have when it comes to making expenditures. It\u2019s also a good way to plan for future spending and include savings. Would you like set a budget ? If you don\u2019t know where to start, it\u2019s less complicated than you might think thanks to our practical budget calculator . It clearly tells you how to proceed and what to list. Feel free to repeat this exercise regularly so that your budget always reflects your reality and you know where your money is going.\nset a budget\nbudget calculator",
