          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Legal\n*Trademark of Visa Int., used under license.\nLaurentian Bank: Laurentian Bank of Canada.\nThe expression \"Bank's prime rate\" refers to the annual interest rate announced by Laurentian Bank from time to time as being its reference rate then in effect for commercial loans, in Canadian dollars. The expression \"Bank's U.S. base rate\" refers to the annual variable interest rate announced by Laurentian Bank from time to time as the reference rate in effect to determine the interest rates applicable to commercial loans in U.S. dollars granted by the Laurentian Bank in Canada and based on a calendar year. Certain conditions apply. The rates mentioned on this site can be modified at any time and without prior notice by Laurentian Bank.\nSubject to change and credit approval by Laurentian Bank. For more information, consult the Section entitled \u201cInformation Box - Summary\u2019\u2019 in the Agreement",
