          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Fees\nWe all bank differently, which is why your Manulife Select Bank \u00ae account has two fee packages. And if you keep a balance of at least $5,000, we\u2019ll waive the monthly or transaction fees .\n\u00ae\n.\nFee options\nWith Manulife Bank Select \u00ae , you have two account fee options for your high interest chequing account\u00a0\u2013 a monthly account and a pay-as-you-go account.\n\u00ae\nOption 1: Monthly-fee account If you do a lot of banking every month, the monthly-fee option may be right for you. This option gives you unlimited transactions for one low monthly fee of $16.95.\nOption 1: Monthly-fee account\nIf you\u2019re 60 years or older the monthly fee is only $9.95. If you maintain a minimum balance of $5,000, you\u2019ll get free banking because we\u2019ll waive the fee.\nUnlimited transactions include:\nDirect deposits\nATM deposits and withdrawals at over 3,500 bank machines (ATMs) across Canada with THE EXCHANGE \u00ae network",
