        {
          "field_name": "prepayment_privileges",
          "candidate_value": "Strategies to pay off your mortgage faster \u2014 without prepayment penalties Looking to become mortgage-free sooner without triggering extra fees? Here are two flexible options that can help you save on interest and gain financial freedom faster: All-in-One account: Combine your mor",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-075979ee4ef116d3",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Strategies to pay off your mortgage faster \u2014 without prepayment penalties\nLooking to become mortgage-free sooner without triggering extra fees? Here are two flexible options that can help you save on interest and gain financial freedom faster:\nAll-in-One account: Combine your mortgage, savings, and income into a single account. With open repayment terms and interest calculated on your daily balance, this setup minimizes interest costs and accelerates your path to full repayment.\nPrepayment privileges on closed mortgages: Many closed mortgages include built-in prepayment options. These allow you to make lump-sum payments or increase your regular payments without triggering a penalty. Using these privileges can significantly reduce your interest costs and shorten your mortgage term.\nIncrease your payment frequency: Depending on the mortgage solution you have chosen, you may be able to",
