          "candidate_value": "If you have a closed-term mortgage , take advantage of one or both of these prepayment options: If you have a closed-term mortgage Make an annual lump-sum payment of up to 20% of your original mortgage amount Once per year, increase your regular mortgage payments by up to 25% 1 I",
